com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.workitem.query.qe
Interface QEQuery

public interface QEQuery

A QEQuery is the root of an object model used by the GUI query builder (QE = Query Editor).

A QEQuery is produced by a QEQueryFactory.

Since:
TEE-SDK-10.1
